										<height>90</height>
										<width>60</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>125 folios (+ 2 unfoliated modern paper and 2 parchment flyleaves at the beginning and at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>17 quires:  i-ix8 (folios 1-72), x6 (folios 73-78), xi-xiii8 (folios 79-102), xiv4 (folios 103-105, 105a), xv-xvi8 (folios 106-121), xvii4 (folios 122-125). No catchwords.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Stained.</p>
									<p>Incomplete at the beginning.</p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="17" writtenLines="17">
									<p>Uniform layout.</p>
									<p>Visible hard-point ruling.</p>
									<p>Hair side and flesh side of folios distinguishable.</p>
									<p>Titles and inital words in larger square characters. </p>
									<p>Last word of a quire repeated at the beginning of a new quire.</p>
									<p>Marginal notes.</p>
									<p>Unfoliated blank leaf after folio 105.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
